The paper deals with capacity limits of a wireless cellular network, which is a topic related to information theory and networking. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes new strategies and bounds for achieving capacity, which involves system-level optimization and control, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of simulations, which suggests that it may also fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.COM (Computers and Society).
